data.description: Wonderful Opportunity to purchase this large 4 bedroom , 2 bath home located just southeast of Columbus in Groveport , Ohio. This 4 level split offers several living spaces where you can relax. Full kitchen with eat in space leads to the oversized and brand new concrete patio. Lower level bedroom with full bath that's perfect for in-law, teen, craft room or workspace stay at home worker. New carpets in living room and hardwood floors leads you to the top level of this four level split. Attached 2 car garage and detached 4 car garage with heaters. Pool with deck and large garden at the rear of the home.
